OL,3,CCatholic PSNI numbers 'isn't good
OL,4,Cenough,' says chief constable
OL,6,FThe number of officers in the PSNI
OL,7,Ffrom a Catholic background "isn't good
OL,8,Fenough", Chief Constable Jon Boutcher
OL,9,Fhas said.
OL,11,FMr Boutcher was speaking to the media
OL,12,Fat a cross-border conference on
OL,13,Forganised and serious crime.
OL,15,FAsked if the PSNI should reinstate the
OL,16,F50:50 recruitment initiative which was
OL,17,Fin place between 2001 and 2011, he
OL,18,Fsaid he wants to use the
OL,19,Forganisation's 25th anniversary to
OL,20,F"have a proper debate about
OL,21,Frecruitment policy".
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@GO]|D@AOU}D@SO]
