OL,3,CCatholic PSNI numbers 'isn't good
OL,4,Cenough,' says chief constable
OL,6,FFigures released by the PSNI last
OL,7,Fmonth showed that the percentage of
OL,8,Fnew Catholic applicants to join the
OL,9,Fforce was at its lowest in more than a
OL,10,Fdecade.
OL,12,FPolice said more than 4,000 people had
OL,13,Fapplied for their latest student
OL,14,Fofficer recruitment campaign, with
OL,15,F65.6% from a Protestant background,
OL,16,F26.7% from a Catholic background and
OL,17,F7.7% undetermined.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
