OL,3,CCatholic PSNI numbers 'isn't good
OL,4,Cenough,' says chief constable
OL,6,FLast week, Sinn Fein said the removal
OL,7,Fof the 50:50 policy, which saw was one
OL,8,FCatholic recruit for every one person
OL,9,Ffrom a Protestant or other background,
OL,10,Fhad a "negative impact" on the number
OL,11,Fof Catholic recruits in policing.
OL,13,FOn Monday Mr Boutcher said: "Everyone
OL,14,Fin our communities, all community
OL,15,Fleaders, all political leaders, all
OL,16,Flocal councillors, priests, bishops,
OL,17,Fteachers, police sports authorities,
OL,18,Fshould all work to stop those people
OL,19,Fdiscouraging people joining the police
OL,20,Fservice.
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@WO]uD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
