CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772640681
OL,3,CCatholic PSNI numbers 'isn't good
OL,4,Cenough,' says chief constable
OL,6,F"In fact, they should actively work to
OL,7,Fencourage people to join the police
OL,8,Fservice."
OL,10,FHe said while "some people do a huge
OL,11,Famount of work to support police"
OL,12,Fthere have been attempts to disrupt
OL,13,Frecruitment initiatives.
OL,15,FMr Boutcher said the PSNI had to
OL,16,Frecently withdraw from a recruitment
OL,17,Ffair at a school because of a bomb
OL,18,Fthreat that was made and that
OL,19,F"dissident Republicans" have made
OL,20,Fthreats to schools he has planned on
OL,21,Fvisiting.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]rD@OOUsD@aO]{D@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
