OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772640681
OL,3,CCatholic PSNI numbers 'isn't good
OL,4,Cenough,' says chief constable
OL,6,F"We've got to address the concerns
OL,7,Fthat people have, legitimate concerns,
OL,8,Fof dissident Republican threats.
OL,10,F"We've got to address the issue in
OL,11,Fsociety that people want to join the
OL,12,Fpolice from a nationalist background,
OL,13,Fand they tell me this, sometimes
OL,14,Fthey're ostracised by their friends,
OL,15,Fthey have to move house.
OL,17,F"That's not a normal society."
